text: Jennifer Eve "Jennie" Garth (born April 3, 1972) is an American actress. Her first starring role was playing Denise in the television series Growing Pains. She starred as Kelly Taylor in Beverly Hills 90210 and also starred in the CW's television series What I Like about You. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Illinois Category:People from Urbana, Illinois
